Bauchi- In it’s determination to unseat the People’s Democratic Party (PDP) led government in Bauchi state in the 2023 governorship election, 80, 000 youth drawn from the 20 local government areas of the state who are members of the All Progressives Congress (APC) have formed a group of like minds called ‘Team APC Bauchi state. Speaking at the official inauguration of the team on Sunday held at Ganjuwa local government, the state chairman and founder of the team Honourable Aminu Lasisi explained that the group is a political movement within the APC aimed at mobilizing popular politicians and supporters to join the party to enable it take back power in the state in the next election. “The aim of creating this team is to embark on massive mobilization of people of the state, who will support and contribute towards the success of APC in the forthcoming 2023 general election.This coalition also aims at bringing unity and stability among members within the party, promoting level playing ground for all members, pacifying aggrieved members and reconciling warring members” EXPOSED - HOW LAGOS DOCTOR DISCOVERED MAJOR REASONS WHY MOST WIVES NOW HEAVILY CHEATS ON THEIR HUSBANDS AND THE PERMANENT SECRET TO SEXUALLY SATISFYING THEIR WIVES. DON'T BE A VICTIM! “For us to achieve great feats in this team of ours, we need to be united.If we are not united, we cannot progress and get whatever we are looking for.We will also try our best to restore aggrieved members back to the party and wherever we are found wanting, we will certainly adjust to restore the governorship seat back to the party” “I want to disabuse the minds of people who are accusing us that we are forming a faction within the party, to bring our own choice of governorship candidate, but that is not true.We still belong to the same APC nationally and belong to everybody.The team is not going to die, rather, it will wax stronger and deliver the dividends of democracy to the people of the state” he said APC Inaugurates C